# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok future hong kong leader tung chee-hwa traveled to beijing wednesday for talks with chinese vice premier and foreign minister qian qichen on the territory 's handover , tung 's office said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (o / office
            :poss (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Tung"
                        :op2 "Chee-hwa")
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                        :ARG1 (o2 / organization
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Hong"
                                    :op2 "Kong"))
                        :time (f / future))))
      :ARG1 (t / travel-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG4 (c / city
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Beijing"))
            :purpose (t2 / talk-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (h / hand-over-02
                        :ARG1 (t3 / territory))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / person
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Qian"
                              :op2 "Qichen")
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c2 / country
                                    :name (n5 / name
                                          :op1 "China"))
                              :ARG2 (p3 / premier
                                    :mod (v / vice)))
                        :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 c2
                              :ARG2 (m / minister
                                    :topic (f2 / foreign)))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (w / wednesday))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok egypt 's former state minister for parliamentary affairs , ahmed salama , has died in a car accident , egypt 's middle east news agency reported monday .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (a / agency
            :mod (n / news)
            :mod (w / world-region
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Middle"
                        :op2 "East"))
            :poss (c / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Egypt")))
      :ARG1 (d / die-01
            :ARG1 (p / person
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Ahmed"
                        :op2 "Salama")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 c
                        :ARG2 (m / minister
                              :topic (a2 / affair-02
                                    :ARG2 (l / legislate-01)))
                        :time (f / former)))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (a3 / accident
                        :mod (c3 / car)))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (m2 / monday))))

                                    :location (c2 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "America")))))

            :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c3 / company
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Metro"
                              :op2 "Atlanta"))
                  :ARG2 (p4 / person
                        :ARG2-of s)))
      :ARG1 (s2 / sue-02
            :ARG0 m
            :ARG1 (p5 / police
                  :mod (c4 / county
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Cobb")))
            :ARG2 (m4 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000
                  :unit (d / dollar))
            :mod (f2 / federal))

            :ARG0 (c6 / claim-01

                        :ARG0 (r / raid-01

                              :poss m)))))
